Class ModifyProductController

java.lang.Object
controllers.ModifyProductController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ModifyProductController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Modifies the product. This includes adding and removing parts from the associated parts list.

      public void initialize​(java.net.URL url, java.util.ResourceBundle resourceBundle)

    • addAssociatedPart

      void addAssociatedPart​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
      Adds associated part from the list of all parts. The part selected will show up in the associated parts table once added
      Parameters:
      event - When button is clicked, part is a added to the associated parts list.

    • cancelProduct

      void cancelProduct​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event) throws java.io.IOException
      Cancels modification. Returns user to the main menu and stops modification. everything is cleared and cancelled.
      Parameters:
      event - The button click that cancels the scene and loads the main menu scene
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException - exception when error is thrown when trying to load

    • removeAssociatedPart

      void removeAssociatedPart​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
      Removes associated part that is selected. Once user confirms, the part is deleted and it is removed from the associated parts table.
      Parameters:
      event - The button initiates deleting the part.

    • saveProduct

      void saveProduct​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
      Saves the modified product. The new product is created and the product is replaced into the inventory.
      Parameters:
      event - the product is saved and the user is sent back to the main menu

    • searchPart

      void searchPart​(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
      This searches parts in the parts table. If the input is a number, the part is searched by ID and if string the part is searched by name. You can search by partial name
      Parameters:
      event - This button will alter the table and show results.

    • isNumeric
